Looks solid,  I was just ready to post about LB VIC but yeah, I'm using it so much now that it's getting to the point where it's almost all I taste because it's so distinct after going on a bender. HS Vanilla Ice Cream or something like CAPS Vanilla Whip Cream would work just fine I bet.&#xD;
&#xD;
I think I'm going to do this with HS VIC .40% 3% LB VIC due to the low % of fruit - Skip the VBIC and sweetener add 50%  WS-23. I'm thinking a possibly a low % of either FA Marshmallow, FLV Cream, or FA Fresh Cream. Although Mango might have to go up higher. Have  you tried it higher as it seems a bit low.
